{"tid":1825560,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"2020年香港即將發生的政治事件","createTime":"2020-01-15T11:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T11:47:25.000Z","uid":149978,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a860592ecb00b7f76bb0cad93eee1739b48e7cfc","tid":1825560,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:30:00.000Z","msg":"1）緊急法和禁蒙面法等緊上訴<br />\n<br />\n最想的上訴結果係，緊急法合憲，但要政府宣佈係緊急狀態先得。咁林鄭和行會就要宣佈香港進入緊急狀態，先可以實施禁蒙面法。緊急狀態解除，自動廢除禁蒙面法。<br />\n<br />\n2）國歌法二讀<br />\n<br />\n政府應該最遲七月前會交上立法會二讀。<br />\n到時睇大家點抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n3）立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n反送中後第一次立法會選舉，非常重要。"},{"pid":"f1e85be8009a6995af7947d08c49449e26115e99","tid":1825560,"uid":41771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:31:25.000Z","msg":"啱呀，要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f438ce5da92c14193dc9718530e202b63c4ad1a1","tid":1825560,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"只要光復立法會，就可以返盤"},{"pid":"c4853189a8ca66f18429a3820b346465dcec0678","tid":1825560,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"港府搞唔掂都仲有人大釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84029ad1ced6f21279b67ccef5248cbccd5d1cbc","tid":1825560,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c4853189a8ca66f18429a3820b346465dcec0678","tid":1825560,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:34:32.000Z","msg":"港府搞唔掂都仲有人大釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"港府那套國歌法惡過大陸套國歌法<br />\n奶共奶得仲勁過中共自己"},{"pid":"58a8c5115cfa230d6206abdac0450afcf4d06e40","tid":1825560,"uid":299937,"like":0,"dislike